Plintissa looked up to see Iron Raptor as she awoke.....she once again got
mad at herslef for getting knocked out.......suddenly, Suukie came crwling
over.......injured bad...... "hey, we won! now we can go home and
have...some fun...." he said.....he was dotted full of bullet holes from all
the shots he recieved durring the battle......there were a few click sounds,
and when Plintissa looked to Sinesis, he was gone!.... "he got away!...."
Plintissa said in shock...... "we'll later make him pay!..." said Suukie,
finishing Plintissa's sentence with a rhyme...... "don't worry, tomorrow is
another..day..." Plintissa spurted out, making a rhyme off of Suukie's
rhyme........ Suukie looked in confusion...he didn't get it.........
